  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dca  \u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The number of children with Covid has also increased",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Deepal Perera, a pediatric specialist at Lady Ridgeway Children's Hospital, Colombo, said that with the increase in the spread of Covid in the society, the number of children infected with Covid is also increasing.",
        "He also mentioned that five children infected with Covid were found at the Lady Ridgeway Children's Hospital in Colombo in recent days.",
        "It is special that these five children have been reported in a background where only one Covid-infected child was not reported.",
        "At the beginning of this year, around 315 children infected with Covid were reported from the Lady Ridgeway Children's Hospital in Colombo, and later the number was reduced to zero, according to hospital sources.",
        "Specialist Dr. Deepal Perera requests the parents to avoid sending their children to school if they have flu-like symptoms.",
        "He mentioned that it is very important to follow health safety measures such as keeping the children away from others if they have such symptoms.",
        "As the spread of Covid has increased in the society in general, the expert said that it is mandatory to wear face masks especially in public places.",
        "In the meantime, since the referral and referral of patients with suspicious symptoms to corona tests has been greatly reduced, it has not been possible to get an accurate measure of the Covid patients in the society today, the health department officials say."
      ],
